  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/8fc4b1f1631df0f4be244037d4fc65a5.poster.avif?t=1743190118\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/8fc4b1f1631df0f4be244037d4fc65a5.webm?t=1743190118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/8fc4b1f1631df0f4be244037d4fc65a5.mp4?t=1743190118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Welcome to the world of Kraktures! A strange world populated by monsters who use creatures called Kraktures to train and fight!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/c60bbc614c9594a7325d7cb1b72a2e90.poster.avif?t=1743190118\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/c60bbc614c9594a7325d7cb1b72a2e90.webm?t=1743190118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/c60bbc614c9594a7325d7cb1b72a2e90.mp4?t=1743190118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Collect, and fight using creatures known as Kraktures in this new, unknown world. You are a human sent to world known as the Great Deep and your goal is to get back home. Along the way you meet new friends, and a sinister group of villians who are up to no good.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/22ab3786f880fe206d50b2fe985e4350.poster.avif?t=1743190118\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/22ab3786f880fe206d50b2fe985e4350.webm?t=1743190118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/22ab3786f880fe206d50b2fe985e4350.mp4?t=1743190118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build your own unique team by picking your Kraktures' stats.</li><li>Select your battle style: A Turn-Based or Realtime RPG!</li><li>Explore up to 12 different islands with different environments and Kraktures.</li><li>Play the way you want with multiple different customization options to make your adventure different each time you play. </li></ul><br><br><br>This is your adventure! Play however you want!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/8fc4b1f1631df0f4be244037d4fc65a5.poster.avif?t=1743190118\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/8fc4b1f1631df0f4be244037d4fc65a5.webm?t=1743190118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/8fc4b1f1631df0f4be244037d4fc65a5.mp4?t=1743190118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Welcome to the world of Kraktures! A strange world populated by monsters who use creatures called Kraktures to train and fight!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/c60bbc614c9594a7325d7cb1b72a2e90.poster.avif?t=1743190118\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/c60bbc614c9594a7325d7cb1b72a2e90.webm?t=1743190118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/c60bbc614c9594a7325d7cb1b72a2e90.mp4?t=1743190118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Collect, and fight using creatures known as Kraktures in this new, unknown world. You are a human sent to world known as the Great Deep and your goal is to get back home. Along the way you meet new friends, and a sinister group of villians who are up to no good.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/22ab3786f880fe206d50b2fe985e4350.poster.avif?t=1743190118\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/22ab3786f880fe206d50b2fe985e4350.webm?t=1743190118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054060/extras/22ab3786f880fe206d50b2fe985e4350.mp4?t=1743190118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build your own unique team by picking your Kraktures' stats.</li><li>Select your battle style: A Turn-Based or Realtime RPG!</li><li>Explore up to 12 different islands with different environments and Kraktures.</li><li>Play the way you want with multiple different customization options to make your adventure different each time you play. </li></ul><br><br><br>This is your adventure! Play however you want!",
